rd.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-grants-bail-to-ex-promoter-of-bhushan-steel-in-money-laundering-case-124090600861_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-grants-bail-to-ex-promoter-of-bhushan-steel-in-money-laundering-case-124090600861_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-grants-bail-to-ex-promoter-of-bhushan-steel-in-money-laundering-case-124090600861_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BArticle%20370%20Is%20History%2C%20Will%20Never%20Come%20Back%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnveiling%20the%20manifesto%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20ruled%20out%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20state%2C%20and%20said%20the%20provision%20has%20now%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20history%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20was%20abrogated%20in%202019%2C%20has%20been%20promised%20in%20the%20manifesto%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20which%20is%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress.%20The%20Assembly%20polls%20will%20be%20the%20first%20since%202014%20and%20are%20also%20being%20keenly%20watched%20to%20gauge%20how%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20feel%20about%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20provision.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20also%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%2C%20including%20Ladakh%2C%20in%202019%20and%20the%20government%20has%20assured%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20be%20given%20statehood%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20former%20state%20has%20been%20very%20important%20to%20the%20BJP%20since%20Independence%20and%20the%20party%20has%20made%20efforts%20since%20then%20to%20keep%20it%20connected%20with%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%202014%2C%20the%20shadow%20of%20separatism%20and%20terrorism%20hung%20over%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Various%20state%20and%20non-state%20actors%20tried%20to%20destabilise%20it%20and%20governments%20adopted%20a%20policy%20of%20appeasement.%20But%2C%20whenever%20the%20history%20of%20India%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20written%2C%20the%20years%20between%202014%20and%202024%20will%20be%20written%20in%20golden%20letters%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%2C%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20we%20saw%20governments%20bowing%20down%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20separatists%20and%20organisations%20like%20the%20Hurriyat.%20In%20these%2010%20years%2C%20Article%20370%20and%2035-A%20(which%20gave%20the%20%C2%A0J%26amp%3BK%20legislature%20the%20right%20to%20define%20permanent%20residents%20and%20give%20them%20special%20privileges)%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20past.%20They%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20asserted%20that%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20under%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20spurred%20development%20in%20the%20state%20and%20said%20he%20had%20read%20the%20National%20Conference's%20manifesto%20as%20well%20as%20noted%20the%20Congress'%20%26quot%3Bsilent%20support%26quot%3B%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20country%3A%20Article%20370%20has%20become%20history.%20It%20can%20never%20come%20back%20and%20we%20will%20never%20allow%20it%20to%20come%20back.%20Because%20Article%20370%20was%20what%20led%20to%20the%20youth%20being%20handed%20guns%20and%20stones%20in%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%