a%20perfect%20society%20and%20patriarchy%20has%20had%20its%20moments%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20challenged.%20From%20lighting%20funeral%20pyres%20to%20presiding%20over%20religious%20rituals%2C%20the%20Bengali%20woman%20has%20continued%20to%20test%20the%20boundaries%20over%20the%20years.%20She%20has%20been%20described%20as%20combative%2C%20domineering%20and%20opinionated.%20There%20have%20been%20some%20bizarre%20descriptors%20too%20-%20like%20'black%20magic%20expert'.%20The%20%26quot%3BBong%26quot%3B%20woman%20has%20laughed%20them%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RG%20Kar%20incident%20threatens%20to%20disturb%20that%20milieu.%20Nearly%20150%20years%20after%20two%20Bengalis%20became%20India's%20first%20women%20graduates%2C%20the%20Bengali%20woman%20feels%20the%20walls%20closing%20in%20on%20her.%20Will%20she%20be%20barred%20from%20night%20shifts%3F%20Treated%20as%20a%20vulnerable%20species%3F%20Need%20men%20to%20escort%20her%20for%20safety%3F%20All%20because%20the%20system%20failed%20her.%20She%20won't%20stay%20home%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20tonight%20or%20any%20other%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fnflol3ng_bengal-protest_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2031-year-old%20doctor%20belonged%20to%20an%20ordinary%20family.%20Through%20her%20determination%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20she%20not%20only%20achieved%20her%20own%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20also%20transformed%20her%20parents'%20future%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20more%20comfortable%20life.%20The%20nameplate%20on%20the%20family's%20home%2C%20with%20only%20her%20name%2C%20captures%20her%20parents'%20pride.%20Then%20one%20night%20shattered%20the%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20doctor's%20grieving%20parents%2C%20many%20women%20-%20and%20men%20-%20see%20their%20own%20parents%2C%20who%20believe%20in%20them%20endlessly%2C%20dream%20for%20them%2C%20live%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20wants%20to%20stand%20by%20them%2C%20come%20what%20may.%20If%20they%20must%20hit%20the%20streets%20daily%20for%20that%2C%20so%20be%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20immense%20anger%20over%20the%20authorities'%20response%20to%20the%20incident%20-%20be%20it%20the%20first%20call%20from%20the%20state-run%20hospital%20to%20the%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20told%20their%20daughter%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20cops%20keeping%20the%20parents%20waiting%20for%20hours%20and%20then%20rushing%20with%20the%20cremation.%20Questions%20have%20been%20asked%20on%20why%20the%20state%20government%20initially%20appeared%20to%20defend%20key%20figures%20suspected%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20a%20cover-up%20attempt%20and%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%20The%20state%20government's%20advisory%20that%20night%20shifts%20must%20be%20avoided%20for%20women%20has%20added%20to%20the%20public%20outcry.%20It%20was%20an%20admission%20that%20the%20administration%20is%20incapable%20of%20protecting%20women%20employees%2C%20say%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ffes76kdg_east-bengal-mohun-bagan-kolkata-horror-pti_625x300_18_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20multiple%20theories%20doing%20the%20rounds%20and%20no%20clear%20answers%2C%20people%20are%20restless.%20Three%20weeks%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20visible%20progress%20has%20ad