24.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66dacf56a0ff598b266525a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225188%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Ukrainian-controlled%20city%20of%20Sudzha%20in%20the%20Kursk%20Region%2C%20Russia%2C%20on%20August%2018%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EEd%20Ram%2FFor%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20army%20chief%20said%20Kyiv%20invaded%20Kursk%20before%20Russia%20could%20launch%20a%20new%20attack%20from%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOleksandr%20Syrskyi%20told%20CNN%20the%20incursion%20forced%20Russia%20to%20redeploy%20forces%20and%20stopped%20its%20advances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20our%20strategy%20is%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Syrskyi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20army%20chief%20said%20Russia%20had%20planned%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20cross-border%20attack%20from%20Kursk%2C%20but%20Kyiv%20got%20there%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20caught%20Russia%20off%20guard%20by%20launching%20an%20incursion%20into%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region%20on%20August%206%2C%20grabbing%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20of%20territory%20in%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Kursk%20incursion%20%26quot%3Breduced%20the%20threat%20of%20an%20enemy%20offensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukraine's%20Commander-in-Chief%2C%20Col.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGen.%20Oleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F09%2F05%2Feurope%2Fukraine-army-chief-kursk-incursion-exclusive-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20prevented%20them%20from%20acting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESyrskyi%20made%20the%20statement%20from%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20near%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-captured-hundreds-square-miles-russian-territory-general-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20under%20a%20week%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20had%20captured%20about%20386%20square%20miles%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20the%20equivalent%20of%20what%20Russia%20has%20captured%20in%20Ukraine%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fu-vijni-nemaye-vidpustok-potribna-vchasna-logistika-ogoloshe-92661%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20that%20one%20of%20the%20operation's%20aims%20was%20to%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuffer%20zone%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20further%20Russian%20attacks%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESyrskyi%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20operation%20aimed%20to%20stop%20Russia%20from%20using%20Kursk%20as%20a%20springboard%20for%20a%20new%20offensive%2C%20and%20to%20force%20it%20into%20redeploying%20its%20military%20from%20other%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Syrskyi%2C%20they%20have%20achieved%20these%20goals%2C%20forcing%20Russia%20to%20redeploy%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20airborne%20assault%20troops%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Kursk%20and%20stopping%20Russian%20advances%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Pokrovsk%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20six%20days%2C%20the%20enemy%20hasn't%20advanced%20a%20single%20meter%20in%20the%20Pokrovsk%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Ukrainian%20forces%20have%20reduced%20Russia's%20capacity%20to%20maneuver%20and%20send%20reinforcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20our%20strategy%20is%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20goals%20being%20pursued%2C%20Syrskyi%20added%2C%20include%20preventing%20cross-border%20shelling%20of%20civilian%20objects%2C%20taking%20prisoners%20of%20war%2C%20and%20improving%20the%20morale%20of%20troops%20and%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Syrskyi%20said%20the%20offensive%20in%20Kursk%20had%20achieved%20some%20of%20its%20goals%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20long%20Ukraine%20can%20retain%20control%20of%20the%20territory%20it%20holds%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20can%20force%20Russia%20to%20redeploy%20enough%20of%20its%20troops%20away%20from%20the%20main%20600-mile%20front%20line%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fzelenskyy-ukraine-russia-territory-seized-putin-kursk-rcna169280%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Zelenskyy%20said%20Ukraine%20is%20planning%20to%20hold%20the%20Russian%20land%20indefinitely%20as%20part%20of%20its%20victory%20plan%2C%20which%20he%20said%20he%20will%20present%20to%20the%20country's%20international%20allies%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-september-5-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20think%20tank%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Russian%20offensive%20operations%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20are%20likely%20to%20conclude%20earlier%20than%20its%20military%20anticipates%20due%20in%20part%20to%20operational%20challenges%20caused%20by%20Ukraine's%20incursion%20into%20Kursk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-planned-attack-from-kursk-ukraine-invaded-first-army-chief-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725622257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66dacf911d8d2deb96b9c225%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-planned-attack-from-kursk-ukraine-invaded-first-army-chief-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20incursion%2