r%20went%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20and%20Ramrattan%20was%20charged%20with%20rape%20and%20impersonating%20a%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20bail%2C%20he%20used%20two%20associates%20to%20report%20fake%20armed%20robberies%20in%20Long%20Island.%20One%20of%20them%20claimed%20that%20Sumasar%20loaded%20a%20shotgun%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20Ramratta%20then%20painted%20Sumasar%20as%20the%20culprit%20by%20leaving%20a%20bullet%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20one%20of%20the%20fake%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20arrested%20Sumasar%20and%20she%20spent%20seven%20months%20in%20Nassau%20County%20Correctional%20Center.%20She%20was%20freed%20in%20December%202010%20after%20an%20informant%20tipped%20off%20the%20Nassau%20County%20District%20Attorney's%20office%20that%20Ramrattan%20framed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e10a0820-2e2e-4f6a-a9ea-f4fc5a1056a6%5C%22%3EJerry%20Ramrattan%20is%20in%20prison%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Indian-American%20man%20with%20short%20black%20hair%20wearing%20a%20blue%20NYPD%20uniform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d5cacb14a5cd1fcc8c7bd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20Jerry%20Ramrattan%20as%20seen%20in%20%26quot%3BWorst%20Ex%20Ever.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202012%2C%20Ramrattan%20was%20convicted%20of%20raping%20Sumasar%20in%202009%2C%20as%20well%20as%20framing%20her%20for%20the%20faked%20armed%20robberies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20his%20convictions%20also%20included%20unlawful%20imprisonment%2C%20perjury%2C%20conspiracy%2C%20and%20falsely%20reporting%20an%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20New%20York%20Assistant%20District%20Attorney%20Frank%20DeGaetano%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2012%2F01%2F05%2Fjustice%2Fnew-york-sentencing%2Findex.html%5C%2