0attack%20on%20the%20lakeside%20town%20in%20Bishnupur%20district%2C%2035%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%20struck%20the%20house%20of%20Manipur's%20first%20Chief%20Minister%20Mairembam%20Koireng%20Singh%2C%20just%20100%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army%20(INA)%20Museum%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Moirang%20town%2C%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20northeast's%20largest%20freshwater%20lake%20Loktak.%20The%20INA%20Museum%20is%20dedicated%20to%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%3B%20Moirang%20town%20is%20where%20the%20INA%20flag%20was%20first%20unfurled%20on%20April%2014%2C%201944%20on%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20INA%20Museum%20was%20the%20likely%20target%20of%20the%20rocket%20attack.%20Residents%20said%20the%20rocket%20came%20from%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elderly%20man%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20was%20offering%20prayers%20when%20shrapnel%20from%20the%20rocket%20hit%20his%20head%2C%20neighbours%20said.%20He%20died%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20with%20blood%20dripping%20on%20the%20floor%20near%20the%20prayer%20items%20such%20as%20leaves%20and%20fruit%20he%20had%20assembled.%20He%20wore%20a%20white%20khudei%20(a%20dhoti-like%20cloth%20of%20the%20Meiteis)%20and%20a%20white%20shawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Moirang%20town%20in%20Manipurs%20Bishnupur%20district%20is%20home%20to%20the%20northeasts%20largest%20freshwater%20lake%20Loktak%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Moirang%20town%20in%20Manipurs%20Bishnupur%20district%20is%20home%20to%20the%20northeasts%20largest%20freshwater%20lake%20Loktak%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fs8uf2rb_loktak-lake_625x300_06_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoirang%20town%20in%20Manipur's%20Bishnupur%20district%20is%20home%20to%20the%20northeast's%20largest%20freshwater%20lake%20Loktak%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20se