Russia%20from%20its%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20enemy's%20goal%20was%20to%20make%20us%20nervous%20and%20worry%20and%20to%20transfer%20troops%20from%20one%20sector%20to%20another%20and%20to%20stop%20our%20offensive%20in%20key%20areas%2C%20primarily%20in%20the%20Donbas%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20at%20a%20forum%20in%20Vladivostok%20Thursday%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-says-ukraines-kursk-incursion-has-failed-slow-donbas-advance-2024-09-05%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20Reuters.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BDid%20it%20work%3F%20No.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Donbas%20is%20the%20eastern%20region%20of%20Ukraine%20that%20is%20the%20main%20front%20line%20of%20Russia's%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20attack%20on%20August%206%2C%20on%20the%20Russian%20border%20region%20of%20Kursk%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-kursk-shows-ability-without-much-west-advice-former-nato-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etook%20Russia's%20military%20commanders%20by%20surprise%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20troops%20advanced%20deep%20into%20Russian%20territory%20and%20took%20hundreds%20of%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Ukraine's%20troops%20still%20occupy%20the%20territory%20which%20comprises%20around%20386%20square%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20caught%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%20Kremlin%20leaders%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20portray%20the%20incursion%20as%20a%20mistake%20by%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20transferring%20rather%20large%20and%20well-trained%20units%20to%20these%20border%20areas%20with%20us%2C%20the%20enemy%20weakened%20itself%20in%20key%20areas%2C%20and%20our%20troops%20accelerated%20offensive%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20argued%20the%20opposite%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20Russia%20that%20was%20forced%20to%20redirect%20its%20bes