nally%20slated%20for%20release%20on%20October%203%2C%202025%2C%20but%20it%20was%20delayed%20by%20a%20year%20until%20October%202%2C%202026%2C%20because%20of%20the%202023%20strikes%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fmovies%2Fmovie-news%2Fthe-batman-ii-delayed-a-year-1235108760%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20fall%20release%20date%20makes%20sense%20for%20the%20moody%20vigilante%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20permanently%20raining%20in%20Gotham.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt'll%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20much%20%26quot%3BThe%20Batman%202%26quot%3B%20makes%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20as%20the%20first%20film%20proved%20successful%20in%20its%20March%202022%20release%2C%20earning%20%24770%20million%20(via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boxofficemojo.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt1877830%2F%5C%22%3EBox%20Office%20Mojo%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERobert%20Pattinson%20and%20Colin%20Farrell%20will%20return%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Batman%202%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20is%20unconfirmed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22921%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robert%20Pattinson%20as%20Bruce%20Wayne.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a1a120d7277f00193f69dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobert%20Pattinson%20as%20Bruce%20Wayne.%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2022%2F04%2Fthe-batman-2-matt-reeves-1235010110%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Pattinson%20has%20signed%20on%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Batman%202%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Reeves%20confirmed%20that%20Farrell%20will%20also%20be%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20probable%20that%20many%20of%20his%20co-stars%20wil