said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20might%20push%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20fantastical%20but%20we%20would%20never%20go%20into%20full%20fantastical.%20It's%20meant%20to%20feel%20quite%20grounded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReeves%20also%20shot%20down%20fan%20speculation%20that%20a%20villain%20called%20Gentleman%20Ghost%20would%20be%20involved%20with%20the%20sequel%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20spiritual%20bad%20guy%20doesn't%20fit%20his%20take%20on%20Gotham.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20you%20won't%20see%20characters%20that%20people%20love.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do.%20Gentleman%20Ghost%20is%20probably%20pushed%20a%20bit%20too%20far%20for%20us%20to%20be%20able%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20do%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20think%20about%20how%20we%20would%20take%20characters%20that%20might%20push%20over%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20the%20fantastical%20and%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20director%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcollider.com%2Fthe-batman-sequel-mr-freeze-matt-reeves-comments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECollider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he'd%20love%20to%20see%20how%20Mr.%20Freeze%20would%20work%20in%20a%20realistic%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20I%20just%20feel%20drawn%20to%20finding%20the%20grounded%20version%20of%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20to%20me%20it%20would%20be%20a%20challenge%20in%20an%20interesting%20way%20to%20try%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20that%20could%20happen%2C%20even%20the%20idea%20of%20something%20like%20Mr.%20Freeze%2C%20that%20such%20a%20great%20story%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20clear%20if%20Barry%20Keoghan%20will%20reprise%20his%20role%20as%20the%20Joker%20after%20his%20brief%20cameo%20alongside%20the%20Riddler%20in%20Arkham%20Asylum.%20But%20the%20Irish%20s