y%20when%20times%20are%20bad%20that%20one%20finds%20out%20who%20is%20standing%20with%20them.%20When%20we%20were%20dragged%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20every%20party%20other%20than%20the%20BJP%20stood%20with%20us%20and%20understood%20our%20pain%20and%20our%20tears%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20proud%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20a%20party%20that%20stands%20up%20against%20misbehaviour%20and%20injustice%20against%20women...%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20that%20we%20will%20work%20for%20them%20with%20the%20same%20intensity%20with%20which%20we%20worked%20in%20wrestling.%20We%20stand%20with%20every%20woman%20who%20finds%20herself%20helpless.%20If%20I%20wanted%2C%20I%20could%20have%20left%20wrestling%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20(during%20the%20protests)%20but%20I%20reached%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20Olympics...%20but%20God%20had%20other%20plans.%20He%20has%20now%20given%20me%20a%20chance%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20my%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Punia%20said%20the%20Congress%20backed%20the%20wrestlers%20during%20their%20protest%20without%20even%20being%20asked%20to%20while%20BJP%20MPs%20ignored%20letters%20seeking%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20raising%20our%20voice%20in%20support%20of%20the%20daughters%20of%20the%20country...%20We%20will%20keep%20working%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20and%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20party%20as%20well%20as%20India.%20Everyone%20was%20happy%20when%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20reached%20the%20finals%20but%20some%20people%20also%20celebrated%20when%20she%20was%20disqualified%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20official%20announcement%20has%20been%20made%20yet%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20is%20expected%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20Julana%20constituency%2C%20held%20by%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%2C%20in%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20polls%20while%20Mr%20Punia%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20fielded%20from%20the%20Badli%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResignation%20From%20Railways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20joining%20the%20Congress%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20resigned%20as%20an%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20(OSD)%20with%20the%20Northern%20Railways%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosting%20a%20photo%20of%20her%20resignation%20letter%2C%20the%20wrestler%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BServing%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20been%20a%20memorable%20and%20proud%20time%20of%20my%20life.%20At%20this%20point%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20separate%20myself%20from%20my%20service%20in%20the%20railways%20and%20have%20submitted%20my%20resignation%20to%20the%20competent%20authorities%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways.%20I%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20the%20Indian%20Railway%20family%20for%20this%20opportunity%20given%20to%20me%20by%20the%20Railways%20in%20the%20service%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phogat's%20popularity%20has%20received%20a%20boost%20recently%20after%20she%20missed%20out%20on%20what%20would%20have%20been%20at%20least%20a%20silver%20medal%20after%20being%20disqualified%20for%20exceeding%20the%20weight%20limit%20by%20100%20grams%20ahead%20of%20the%20final%20bout%20in%20the%2050%20kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20event.%20The%20grit%20shown%20by%20the%20wrestler%20in%20defeating%20reigning%20gold%20medallist%20Yui%20Susaki%20of%20Japan%20and%20going%20on%20to%20enter%20the%20final%20had%20earned%20her%20plaudits%20while%20her%20eventual%20disqualification%20had%20broken%20a%20billion%20hearts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers'%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phogat%20announced%20her%20retirement%20from%20wrestling%20after%20the%20disqualification%20and%20all%20eyes%20had%20been%20on%20her%20next%20steps.%20Last%20week%2C%20she%20reached%20the%20Haryana-Punjab%20Shambhu%20border%2C%20extended%20her%20support%20to%20farmers%20staging%20a%20protest%20for%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops%20and%20said%20she%20stood%20with%20them%20as%20their%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20agitation%20completes%20200%20days%20today.%20I%20pray%20to%20God%20that%20you%20get%20what%20you%20have%20come%20here%20for%20-%20your%20right%2C%20for%20justice...Your%20daughter%20stands%20with%20you.%20I%20also%20urge%20the%20government...%20we%20too%20are%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%2C%20if%20we%20raise%20our%20voices%20it%20is%20not%20political%20every%20time...You%20should%20hear%20them...What%20they%20are%20demanding%20is%20not%20unlawful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoost%20To%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entry%20of%20the%20wrestlers%20into%20the%20Congress%20is%20expected%20to%20give%20it%20a%20boost%20as%20Ms%20Phogat%20is%20seen%20to%20enjoy%20support%20among%20farmers%2C%20who%20make%20up%20a%20significant%20voting%20bloc%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20farmers'%20anger%20against%20the%20BJP%20will%20help%20it%20dislodge%20the%20party%20from%20a%20state%20it%20has%20ruled%20since%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20also%20hope%20that%20Mr%20Punia%20and%20Ms%20Phogat%20joining%20the%20party%20will%20give%20it%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20its%20negotiations%20with%20INDIA%20ally%20AAP%20in%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%2090%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20an%20in-principle%20agreement%20regarding%20an%20alliance%20had%20been%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20stalemate%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20with%20the%20AAP%20seeking%2010%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20willing%20to%20give%20up%20only%20five%20to%20seven.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpbeat%20after%20winning%20five%20out%20of%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20this%20year%20after%20the%20BJP's%20clean%20sweep%20in%202019%2C%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20was%20reluctant%20to%20part%20with%20any%20Assembly%20constituencies%20but%20the%20push%20for%20a%20tie-up%20has%20reportedly%20come%20from%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20maintained%20that%20it%20will%20ensure%20there%20is%20no%20division%20of%20votes%20and%20give%20the%20party%20its%20best%20possible%20chance%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDifferences%20within%20the%20Congress%20have%20reportedly%20delayed%20its%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20facing%20pushback%20and%20a%20rebellion%20since%20it%20did%20so%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20Energy%20Minister%20Ranjit%20Chautala%20and%20MLA%20Lakshman%20Napa%20quitting%20the%20party%20after%20being%20denied%20tickets.%20Mr%20Chautala%20has%20said%20he%20will%20contest%20as%20an%20Independent%20and%20Mr%20Napa%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20be%20joining%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chautala%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal%20Chaudhary%2C%20one%20of%20Haryana's%20tallest%20leaders%2C%20who%20served%20as%20chief%20minister%20twice%20and%20was%20also%20a%20deputy%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725618720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fr1m903n_vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-congress_625x300_06_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-join-congress-ahead-of-haryana-elections-6504268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shaking%20up%20the%20political%20landscape%20in%20Haryana%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%2C%20wrestlers%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20have%20joined%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-join-congress-ahead-of-haryana-elections-6504268%22%2C%