-6503079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20EasyJet%20flight%2C%20bound%20for%20Kos%20International%20Airport%20in%20Greece%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20at%20Munich%20International%20Airport%20after%20an%20allegedly%20drunk%20passenger%20caused%20midair%20chaos%20and%20terrorised%20others%20onboard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-easyjet-flight-forced-to-make-emergency-landing-after-drunk-passenger-causes-chaos-mid-air-6503079%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Boost%20In%20Sustainable%20Energy%20Spending%20By%20Government%3A%20Pralhad%20Joshi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPralhad%20Joshi%2C%20Minister%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%2C%20today%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20spent%20significantly%20on%20sustainable%20energy%20for%20a%20greener%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20India%20Sustainability%20Mission%20-%20Conclave%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20nature.%20India%20treats%20nature%20as%20God.%20Reforms%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20have%20put%20India%20very%20high%20in%20the%20world%20on%20several%20green%20energy%20barometers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20installed%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20has%20surged%20by%20an%20impressive%20165%20per%20cent%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20rising%20from%2075.52%20GW%20to%20over%20203%20GW%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20said.%20This%20surge%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20increase%20in%20renewable%20energy%20generation%2C%20which%20grew%20from%20193.5%20billion%20units%20(BU)%20to%20360%20BU%20between%202013%20and%202024%20-%20an%2086%20per%20cent%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20aspect%20of%20the%20renewable%20energy%20growth%20story%20is%20that%20the%20solution%20is%20being%20pr