ecreased.%20Solar%20power%20tariffs%20for%20grid-connected%20plants%20dropped%20by%2076%25%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20from%20Rs%2010.95%20per%20unit%20in%202010-11%20to%20Rs%202.60%20per%20unit%20in%202023-24%2C%20making%20solar%20energy%20more%20accessible%20and%20cost-effective%20for%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725606720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4q5pai4g_pralhad-joshi-_625x300_06_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-boost-in-sustainable-energy-spending-by-government-pralhad-joshi-6503194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20Minister%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%2C%20today%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20spent%20significantly%20on%20sustainable%20energy%20for%20a%20greener%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-boost-in-sustainable-energy-spending-by-government-pralhad-joshi-6503194%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Yellow%20Earth%E2%80%99%20Restoration%20Decorates%20Pingyao%20Film%20Festival%208th%20Edition%20Lineup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725606060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FYellow-Earth-MBDYEEA_EC001-3x2lcr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236132704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20restored%20edition%20of%20Chen%20Kaige%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CYellow%20Earth%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20the%20selection%20for%20the%208th%20edition%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20boutique%20Pingyao%20International%20Film%20Festival.%20The%20film%2C%20which%20helped%20put%20Chinese%20art-house%20cinema%20on%20the%20map%20overseas%20and%20signaled%20a%20new%20era%20of%20Chinese%20directors%2C%20now%20referred%20to